{{Aqbu ( Bgayet )}}
{{Imezdaɣ belɛen abrid aɣelnaw uṭṭun 26}}
Imezdaɣ n lḥuma n « SONATRACH » deg Weqbu lwilaya n Bgayet, belɛen abrid aɣelnaw uṭṭun 26 i icudden ger Lezzayer akked Bgayet, iḍelli akked wass-a n letnayen 9 ctember i wakken ad d-seknen lɣiḍ-nnsen mgal lmaḍra i d-yessegray lbarud yeṭṭerḍiqen di lkaryar » carrière » id yezgan di tama n « SONATRACH ». D ayen i yeǧǧan ixxamen ad cqeqqen. Γef -aya imesbaniyen-agi sutren deg iḍebren teɛna temsalt aɣlaq n lkaryar-agi.
Abelleɛ n webrid yesserfa nezzeh ixeddamen akked inelmaden yuɣalen iḍelli ɣer iɣerbazen.
C.W.
